{
  "texts": [
    "We fixed the prompt encoder since it can already encode the bounding box prompt.",
    "All the trainable parameters in the image encoder and mask decoder were updated during training.",
    "Specifically, the number of trainable parameters for the image encoder and mask decoder are 89,670,912 and 4,058,340, respectively.",
    "The bounding box prompt was simulated from the expert annotations with a random perturbation of 0-20 pixels.",
    "The loss function is the unweighted sum between dice loss and cross-entropy loss, which has been proven to be robust in various segmentation tasks 1."
  ]
}